    <string name = "helpScreen_instructionsTitle">How to Play the Game</string>
    <string name = "instructions_stepZero">Game Goal: Find all hidden mines with the fewest amount of scans. </string>
    <string name = "instructions_stepOne">1. Tap on any cell in the game grid to inspect it.</string>
    <string name = "instructions_stepTwo">2.1 If there is a milk carton on that cell, then it will reveal itself.</string>
    <string name = "instructions_stepThree">2.2 If it is an empty cell, the vertical and horizontal columns of that the cell will be scanned.</string>
    <string name = "instructions_stepFour">2.3 After the scan, a number will appear in the selected cell which tells you how many milk cartons are nearby in either the cell\'s horizontal or vertical columns. </string>
    <string name="instructions_stepFive">3. Continue tapping on different cells to find all the milk cartons.</string>
    <string name="instructions_endNote">Note: Finding a milk carton in a cell will not count towards the scan number,
        only selecting empty cells will count towards the number of scans.</string>

